## 3 Add item
Request
POST /api/v1/update-new-item
```
{
	"customerId": 1,
	"productId": 2,
	"quantity": 2
}
```
Response
```
{
    "status": "Success",
    "message": "Add item success",
    "data": {
        "id": {
            "cartId": 1,
            "productId": 2
        },
        "quantityWished": 2,
        "dateAdded": "2022-08-31T16:08:04.130+00:00",
        "totalAmount": 82650.00
    }
}
```
## 4 Update the item if it already exists, otherwise add item
Request
POST /api/v1/update-new-item
```
{
	"customerId": 1,
	"productId": 2,
	"quantity": 3
}
```
Response
```
{
    "status": "Success",
    "message": "Add item success",
    "data": {
        "id": {
            "cartId": 1,
            "productId": 2
        },
        "quantityWished": 5,
        "dateAdded": "2022-08-31T16:09:16.279+00:00",
        "totalAmount": 206625.00
    }
}
```
### Handle the case where customer id is not exists
Request
POST /api/v1/update-new-item
```
{
    "customerId": 15,
    "productId": 2,
    "quantity": 3
}
```
Response
```
{
    "status": "failed",
    "message": "Customer id is not exists",
    "data": ""
}
```
### Handle the case where product id is not exists
Request
POST /api/v1/update-new-item
```
{
    "customerId": 5,
    "productId": 13,
    "quantity": 3
}
```
Response
```
{
    "status": "failed",
    "message": "Product id is not exists",
    "data": ""
}
```
## 5 Get list of item's info by parameter
Request
GET /api/v1/info-cart-item
```
{
    "customerId": 1,
    "nameProduct": "product2",
    "offset": 0,
    "limit": 1
}
```
Response
```
{
    "status": "ok",
    "message": "ok",
    "data": [
        {
            "cartId": 1,
            "productId": 2,
            "nameProduct": "product2",
            "type": "12",
            "size": "12",
            "quantity": 5,
            "price": 41325.00,
            "totalAmount": 206625.00,
            "dateAdded": "2022-08-31T16:09:16.279+00:00"
        }
    ]
}
```
Request
GET /api/v1/info-cart-item
```
{
    "customerId": 1,
    "nameProduct": "product2",
    "offset": 1,
    "limit": 2
}
```
Response
```
{
    "status": "ok",
    "message": "ok",
    "data": []
}
```